<Body>
	<Title>油罐爆炸起火燃烧3小时</Title>
	<ReportTime type="absTime">2009年08月02日</ReportTime>
	<Content>
		<Paragraph><Sentence><Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e1"><Participant sid="s1">本报</Participant><Location lid="l1">东莞</Location><Denoter did="d1" type="statement">讯</Denoter></Event>（记者代希奎、黄维）</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e2"><Time tid="t2" type="relTime">昨日上午9时50分左右</Time>，<Location lid="l2">麻涌镇南洲村东莞市港航船舶清污有限公司</Location>发生一起<Denoter did="d2" type="emergency">火灾</Denoter>事故</Event>，<Event eid="e3"><Time tid="t3" type="relTime">12时40分许</Time><Object oid="o3">火势</Object>被<Denoter did="d3" type="stateChange">扑灭</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e4"><Participant sid="s4">消防部门</Participant>先后<Denoter did="d4" type="operation">出动</Denoter>了<Object oid="o4">17辆消防车</Object>支援</Event>,<Event eid="e5"><Denoter did="d5" type="emergency">事故</Denoter></Event><Event polarity="negative" eid="e6">没有造成人员<Denoter did="d6" type="stateChange">伤亡</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e7"><Time tid="t7" type="relTime">目前</Time>火灾事故<Object oid="o7">原因</Object>尚在<Denoter did="d7" type="operation">调查</Denoter>当中</Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>


　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e8">目击者<Participant sid="s8">吴先生</Participant><Denoter did="d8" type="statement">称</Denoter></Event>最初爆炸起火的油罐较大，火势较猛，一时难以控制。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e9">在<Time tid="t9" type="relTime">上午10时45分左右</Time>，<Object oid="o9">第2个油罐</Object>也被<Denoter did="d9" type="action">引燃</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e10">在<Time tid="t10" type="relTime">11时30分左右</Time>也发生了<Denoter did="d10" type="emergency">爆炸</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>

　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e11"><Denoter did="d11" type="emergency">火灾</Denoter>发生</Event>后，<Event eid="e12"><Participant sid="s12">消防部门</Participant>先后<Denoter did="d12" type="operation">出动</Denoter>了<Object sid="s12">17辆消防车</Object></Event>,<Event eid="e13">经过<Time tid="t13" type="timeInterval">近3小时</Time>的<Denoter did="d13" type="operation">扑救</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e14"><Participant sid="s14">消防人员</Participant>在<Time tid="t14" type="relTime">12时40分左右</Time>成功将<Object oid="o14">火势</Object><Denoter did="d14" type="stateChange">扑灭</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>

　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e15">经<Denoter did="d15" type="operation">调查</Denoter></Event>，事故现场主要有两个储油罐着火，火场过火面积约400平方米。</Sentence><Sentence>由于起火地点远离居民区，<Event eid="e16"><Denoter did="d16" type="emergency">事故</Denoter></Event><Event polarity="negative" eid="e17">没有造成人员<Denoter did="d17" type="stateChange">伤亡</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e18"><Denoter did="d18" type="emergency">事</Denoter></Event>后，<Event eid="e19"><Participant sid="s19">消防大队</Participant>对<Location lid="l19">火灾事故现场</Location>进行<Denoter did="d19" type="action">洒水</Denoter>降温处理</Event>，<Event eid="e20">并<Denoter did="d20" type="operation">派</Denoter><Participant oid="o20" sid="s21">专人</Participant></Event><Event eid="e21"><Denoter did="d21" type="action">留驻</Denoter><Location lid="l21">现场</Location></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
	
